      "playtime_at_review": 580,
      "review_text": "This is a very fun and great addition to the Five Nights at Freddy's franchise! There are three different types of gameplay that all mesh well to form a very engaging gameplay loop. The story is captivating, bittersweet, and is, what I consider, to be the end of FNaF. The game has bits and pieces of replayability here and there, but once you get the \"Completionist\" Certificate (the \"Good Ending\"), there's really no point in replaying it, unless for the lore. Other than that, I highly recommend this game!",
      "timestamp_created": 1774117293
